# {{VAULT_NAME}} -- Conventions for Aider

This is an ideaverse-OS vault. Aider should read these files at session start to understand the user's identity, workflow, and current priorities.

## Read first

| File | Role |
|---|---|
| `00-agentic-OS/soul.md` | Behavioral constraints (universal rules) |
| `00-agentic-OS/me.md` | Identity dossier |
| `00-agentic-OS/user.md` | Workflow + tooling preferences |
| `00-agentic-OS/compass.md` | Current goals + priorities |
| `00-agentic-OS/memory.md` | Append-only decision log |
| `00-agentic-OS/runbook.md` | Skill chains for common intents |

All have `auto_inject: true` frontmatter.

## Coding conventions

Refer to `00-agentic-OS/soul.md` for ASCII / no-em-dash / file-naming rules.
Refer to `00-agentic-OS/user.md` for harness preferences and tool stack.

